</ul>
<p><strong>4.3 You understand and agree that:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>4.3.1 In the event that Xiaomi suspects that the User has violated this Agreement, the license may be revoked, or other appropriate measures within the scope of this Agreement may be taken.</li>
<li>4.3.2 If the User publishes information upon the platform which may infringe upon any person's legal rights or violates this Agreement, the information will be deleted directly.</li>
<li>4.3.3 In the event of damage to a third party by a User who violates this Agreement, the User shall assume liability in their own name and understand that Xiaomi shall not be responsible for any loss or damage.</li>
