<p>5.1 The User must have a required mobile terminal device with network access capabilities to use telecom value-added services, and will be responsible for fees related to network access on mobile terminal devices as well as communications fees, information fees, and other related fees charged by third party providers (including but not limited to fees charged by service providers). If you are using value-added telecom services, we recommend that you confirm the related costs with your telecom value-added service provider.</p>
<p>5.2 <strong>Xiaomi and its Cooperators are not responsible for any loss caused by third parties, such as communication line failure, technical problems, network or mobile terminal equipment failure, system instability, and other events of force majeure.</strong></p>
<p>5.3 This Software, like most Internet software and services, may be subject to various security problems brought about by users, network connection quality, social environment, etc. For example, publishing personal information may result in real-life harassment; other software products downloaded and installed or other websites visited by you may contain viruses (such as "Trojan horses") such that security risks are brought about and the features of this Software are affected. To avoid damage and harassment, you are advised to be aware of the possible security risks and take the necessary measures to prevent them.</p>
<p>5.4 <strong>Xiaomi may cooperate with third parties and use third party systems and software to provide the required services related to the Software. Xiaomi cannot guarantee that data generated with third-party involvement is secure, accurate, or without risk. Xiaomi shall not bear any responsibility for any loss or damage in such cases.</strong></p>
