<p>7.1 Xiaomi owns all the intellectual property rights to the Software. Any copyright, trademarks, patent rights, trade secrets, and other intellectual property rights related to this Software and all its related content (including but not limited to text, images, audio, video, charts, interface and layout design, relevant data, or electronic documents) belong to Xiaomi and are protected by local laws and regulations and corresponding international treaties.</p>
