<h3>8. Modification of this Agreement</h3>
<p>8.1 Xiaomi has the right to amend the clauses of this Agreement if and when necessary. Once any clause of this Agreement is amended, the amended clause will be published on the relevant page. If you do not agree with the amendments made, you should stop using this Service. Your continued use of the Service will constitute your acceptance of any changes or modifications of the Agreement.</p>
<p>8.2 Xiaomi and its partners have the right to modify or change the paid services, payment standards and methods, service fees, and terms of service at any time. We may charge for certain parts of the service immediately or after a certain period. If you refuse to pay these fees, you will not be able to continue to use the relevant services after fees are instated. We will notify you about changes related to payments via email or other methods.</p>
<h3>9. Applicable law and legal disputes</h3>
