<p>9.2 The User and Xiaomi agree that any disputes arising from the use of this Service shall be resolved through negotiation. Any legal disputes that cannot be resolved through negotiation will be subject to the non-exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in the jurisdiction where the User is located.</p>
